OL,3,CSteve Wright's cause of death revealed
OL,4,Cas ruptured stomach ulcer
OL,6,FRadio 2 DJ Steve Wright died from a
OL,7,Fruptured ulcer in his stomach,
OL,8,Faccording to his death certificate.
OL,10,FVeteran BBC radio broadcaster Wright,
OL,11,Fone of the most familiar voices on the
OL,12,Fairwaves in the UK, died at the age of
OL,13,F69 in February.
OL,15,FThe causes of death were acute
OL,16,Fperitonitis and a perforated gastric
OL,17,Fpeptic ulcer, the certificate obtained
OL,18,Fby the BBC says.
