OL,6,FPeritonitis is an infection of the
OL,7,Flining of the stomach, according to
OL,8,Fthe NHS.
OL,10,FA perforated ulcer is a rarer
OL,11,Fcomplication when the lining of the
OL,12,Fstomach splits open.
OL,14,FThe Metropolitan Police previously
OL,15,Fsaid Wright's death at a flat in the
OL,16,FMarylebone area of central London "was
OL,17,Funexpected, but is not being treated
OL,18,Fas suspicious".
