OL,6,FWright first joined BBC Radio 1 in
OL,7,F1980 to host a Saturday evening show
OL,8,Fand held various positions including
OL,9,Fan afternoon show and a breakfast show
OL,10,Fat the station.
OL,12,FHe had a stint at commercial radio
OL,13,Fbefore returning to BBC Radio 2 in
OL,14,F1996 to host Steve Wright's Saturday
OL,15,FShow and Sunday Love Songs and three
OL,16,Fyears later presented Steve Wright In
OL,17,FThe Afternoon every weekday on Radio 2.
