OL,6,FWright stepped down in September 2022,
OL,7,Freplaced by Scott Mills in a schedule
OL,8,Fshake-up, but Wright continued to
OL,9,Fpresent Sunday Love Songs on BBC Radio
OL,10,F2.
OL,12,FMichael Ball has since replaced Wright
OL,13,Fas the host of a Sunday love songs
OL,14,Fshow, which has been retitled Love
OL,15,FSongs With Michael Ball.
OL,17,FIt was previously confirmed no inquest
OL,18,Fwill be held into Wright's death.
